Campus and around the country.

00:03:16.670 --> 00:03:21.810
For more information,
visit loc.gov/poetry.

00:03:21.810 --> 00:03:23.550
And so now I'm going
to sit down,

00:03:23.550 --> 00:03:26.510
and there will be a little
bit of rejiggering my mic,

00:03:26.510 --> 00:03:29.520
and then Jennifer Foerster
